<section id="about">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row mt centered">
			<div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
				<h1>About</h1>
				<h3>Let's get down to brass tacks.</h3>
			</div>
		</div><!-- /row -->
		
		<div class="row mt centered">
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<img src="assets/icon_10412/icon_10412_modified.png" width="180" alt="">
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->

			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<h4>The Crux</h4>
				<p><b>Vital Patch</b> is a revolutionary fall-detection device for seniors. It's easy to wear, unobtrusive, and gives seniors the independence they deserve while offering peace of mind to their families. It consists of a pulse monitor, thermometer, accelerometer, gyroscope, and wifi transceiver all packed in a comfortable bandage that is easily removable from the skin.</p>				
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->
		</div><!-- /row -->

		<div class="row mt centered">			
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<h4>Falling Alerts</h4>
				<p>Using a state of the art algorithm, <b>Vital Patch</b> is able to detect when falls occur.  It will then send out an alert to let the proper people know that help is needed.  And the great part is, you can decide who to alert; some common examples are your loved ones, a caretaker, or 911.</p>				
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<img src="assets/icon_18418/icon_18418_modified.png" width="180" alt="">
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->
		</div><!-- /row -->

		<div class="row mt centered">
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<img src="assets/icon_144/icon_144_modified.png" width="180" alt="">
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->

			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<h4>Peace of Mind</h4>
				<p><b>Vital Patch</b> keeps track of your pulse and temperature vitals, allowing you and your loved ones to be able to check in with how you're doing.  Now, you can see how healthy you are, and how your health has changed over time.  Peace of mind for you, peace of mind for your family.</p>
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->
		</div><!-- /row -->
	</div><!-- /container -->
</section>

