			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->

			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<h4>Number One Cause of Injury Deaths</h4>
				<p>In seniors, falls are the number one cause of fractures, hospital admissions for trauma, loss of independence, and injury deaths.</p>
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->
		</div><!-- /row -->

		<div class="row mt centered">
			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<h4>Signs of Other Medical Issues</h4>
				<p>Falls can be a sign of a new medical problem that needs attention, such as diabetes or changes in blood pressure. Falls can also be a sign of problems with medications or eyesight that can be easily corrected once detected.</p>
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->

			<div class="col-lg-6">
				<img src="assets/icon_2384/icon_2384.png" width="180" alt="">					
			</div><!--/col-lg-3 -->
